description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps the Weekend in the NFL. Who had the worst loss of the weekend? Peter King tells us which team he thinks made the loudest statement. And Carson Palmer discusses whether he thinks Cam Newton is a Hall of Famer.
